objective:
This course will specifically target rhetorical patterns and grammar for writing essays and in academic contexts. In class we will:

‧	Deepen our understanding of the connection among reading, critical thinking and 
        writing;
‧	Create an awareness of and develop skills for writing coherent, cohesive paragraphs;
‧	Practice and master the multi-paragraph essay
‧	Practice the various rhetorical modes: exemplification, cause-and-effect, and  
        comparison/contrast;
‧	Increase academic vocabulary;
‧	Establish effective strategies for our personal writing process;
‧	Learn and practice strategies for effective academic presentations;
‧	Write a 1-2 page comparison/contrast essay.
